{"tid":913041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"山羊生出「半人半豬」怪物 村民：被詛咒的惡魔","createTime":"2018-11-23T06:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T07:39:24.000Z","uid":167451,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"995b1f84456c22286c33f03679a4c5b2c4a1f3bf","tid":913041,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:15:47.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】菲律賓民答那峨島的一個小農場，日前有隻母山羊產下一隻外型酷似「半人半豬」的怪胎，引起村民恐慌，認為它是被「詛咒的惡魔」會帶來厄運。<br />\n<br />\n這頭懷孕的母山羊，11月初在蘇丹庫達拉省（Sultan Kudarat）的一個小農場內分娩。當時，母山羊通過剖腹手術產下兩胎，其中一胎樣子正常，但另一胎全身無毛，看起來像一頭豬，皮膚有淡粉色的光澤，又混合著一些人類的特徵，還有類似肚臍的疤痕。<br />\n<br />\n40歲女農民雷皮克（Josephine Repique）表示，這生物「看起來像是一頭豬，混著人類的特徵。沒有人知道牠是什麼，但不是隻羊」。<br />\n<br />\n村民表示，當這個「怪胎」從母羊體內被取出時，大家都發出恐怖的尖叫。完全無法解釋它怎麼會長成這樣。附近的村民全部跑到農場，爭相看這只奇怪的生物。最後，這對山羊母子都沒能活下來，這也引起了村民們的恐懼，大家擔心這是一隻被詛咒的「變種惡魔」，會給村子帶來厄運。<br />\n<br />\n對此，菲律賓大學動物科學研究院的薩爾塞斯博士（Agapita Salces）表示，母山羊可能是被蚊子叮咬後，感染了裂谷熱（Rift Valley fever），才導致胎兒發育畸形。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CqEzP73.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCqEzP73.png&h=3ed27eb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource:- <a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B1%B1%E7%BE%8A%E7%94%9F%E5%87%BA-%E5%8D%8A%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%8A%E8%B1%AC-%E6%80%AA%E7%89%A9-%E6%9D%91%E6%B0%91-%E8%A2%AB%E8%A9%9B%E5%92%92%E7%9A%84%E6%83%A1%E9%AD%94-035700043.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25BE%258A%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2587%25BA-%25E5%258D%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258D%258A%25E8%25B1%25AC-%25E6%2580%25AA%25E7%2589%25A9-%25E6%259D%2591%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25A9%259B%25E5%2592%2592%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2583%25A1%25E9%25AD%2594-035700043.html&d=9VGb%2F0e%2BiPoaNMotUy%2Btq%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=4e951a75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B1%B1%E7%BE%8A%E7%94%9F%E5%87%BA-%E5%8D%8A%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%8A%E8%B1%AC-%E6%80%AA%E7%89%A9-%E6%9D%91%E6%B0%91-%E8%A2%AB%E8%A9%9B%E5%92%92%E7%9A%84%E6%83%A1%E9%AD%94-035700043.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真的假的？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790f35e68ee6450e4e24b49411ba629baa3c93dc","tid":913041,"uid":163291,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:17:45.000Z","msg":"對此，菲律賓大學動物科學研究院的薩爾塞斯博士（Agapita Salces）表示，母山羊可能是被蚊子叮咬後，感染了裂谷熱（Rift Valley fever），才導致胎兒發育畸形。<br />\n<br />\n95%鳩up<br />\n最後一段先講少少事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75a242829893f0b5f3ef75bc12e768ad59e6a48","tid":913041,"uid":167451,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:17:46.000Z","msg":"好得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f813c2cbe784a345df0f29e592dc8ed9c3f07e","tid":913041,"uid":23829,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:20:09.000Z","msg":"懷仔咁款"},{"pid":"5fe7e0f2c23ed5b70354bd40ef0a3dd865297f85","tid":913041,"uid":212246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:24:37.000Z","msg":"ManBearPig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895253f4481375e3f33bec84cfd6e6dccac82c94","tid":913041,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:25:20.000Z","msg":"邊位手足好出黎認左佢"},{"pid":"59ebe4b33cbca0e592d25a24ae112cc71f0af9c5","tid":913041,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:25:38.000Z","msg":"會唔會係人獸交🤔🤔🤔🤔"},{"pid":"4115385030f4d46c4508f45784b23e9fdfdaf81e","tid":913041,"uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NpOEgSo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNpOEgSo.png&h=8c322fb2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cea9380bf923c4f68a26738adf23aace5488cb3e","tid":913041,"uid":134231,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:31:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係人獸交🤔🤔🤔🤔</blockquote><br />\n小學畢業未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aab8e0ae69b8026405cd7937a417af1ba5813d3","tid":913041,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cea9380bf923c4f68a26738adf23aace5488cb3e","tid":913041,"uid":134231,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:31:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係人獸交🤔🤔🤔🤔</blockquote><br />\n小學畢業未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:32:52.000Z","msg":"點解咁講"},{"pid":"7f0179580f02ce50cfb19d9f93dc93235258146b","tid":913041,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:35:10.000Z","msg":"好似好假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ad52e0f57139e246ebfbfd6450901ec6f6b843","tid":913041,"uid":15914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4115385030f4d46c4508f45784b23e9fdfdaf81e","tid":913041,"uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NpOEgSo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNpOEgSo.png&h=8c322fb2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:35:43.000Z","msg":"咩漫?"},{"pid":"e8aa397a10a287a581a4410bad75e6f92fa2c932","tid":913041,"uid":134231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:36:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會係人獸交🤔🤔🤔🤔</blockquote><br />\n小學畢業未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>點解咁講</blockquote><br />\nsperm同egg嘅結構差咁遠<br />\n唔會結合到"},{"pid":"858e2dce7f6156a394144cf1d6f8268d8c95210b","tid":913041,"uid":118480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4115385030f4d46c4508f45784b23e9fdfdaf81e","tid":913041,"uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NpOEgSo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNpOEgSo.png&h=8c322fb2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:42:43.000Z","msg":"黑山羊，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e7bbaaf03b450ef2e9abf3a8e2663867de74fa","tid":913041,"uid":33864,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T07:39:24.000Z","msg":"在一個古老的山鄉，發現了一個古老的村落。由於他們世世代代和外界隔絕，宛如桃源中人，外界對他們產生了濃厚的興趣。於是一個漂亮的女記者前往這落後的山鄉，去採訪當地人。<br />\n<br />\n她採訪的對象是一個六十多歲的老者，知道他們世世代代與世隔絕的生活以後，女記者驚訝，繼而是好奇，於是她打算描寫一下他們與世隔絕生活中的喜怒哀樂。<br />\n<br />\n「請問，多年來，您最高興的一件事情是甚麽？」，好奇的女記者問。<br />\n<br />\n「有一年冬天，隔壁老三家的羊走失了。」老頭說。<br />\n<br />\n「羊走失了，有甚麽值得高興的嗎？」女記者更好奇了。<br />\n<br />\n「羊丟了以後，我們幾十個人打着火把上山去找，找了三天三夜，終於在後山的一個角落裏面找到了」，老者吸了口煙，眯縫着眼睛回味無窮的說。<br />\n<br />\n「找到後怎麽了？」女記者好奇的問。<br />\n<br />\n「找到的時候天已經很晚了，我門在雪堆裏面紮了帳篷休息。外面的風很大。我們感到很無聊。於是大家就輪流上那只羊。好爽！」<br />\n<br />\n女記者顯然感到有點尷尬，她想避開這個話題。於是她打斷老者的話，問有沒有其他高興的事情？<br />\n<br />\n「有一年冬天，前邊老馬家的新媳婦在山裏面走失了。」老者說。<br />\n<br />\n「找到了嗎？」女記者追問。<br />\n<br />\n「我們幾十個人找了三天三夜，終於在後山的角落裏找到了。於是我們按下帳篷休息。冬天的晚上的風很大。我們大家都很無聊。於是我們就輪流上老馬他家的新媳婦，別提多爽了。」老者說着敲了敲手中的旱煙袋。<br />\n<br />\n女記者感到更尷尬了。她決定避開這個話題。於是她問到，在這幾十年與世隔絕的生活中究竟有沒有甚麽值得悲傷的事情？<br />\n<br />\n老者的臉色突變，手也開始顫抖，幾乎抓不住手中的旱煙。深陷的眼眶中滾出了兩滴渾濁的淚。嘴唇哆嗦了好幾下，他的身體也似乎在顫抖。沈默良久，他說：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「一年冬天，我走失了！」"}]}